desc: What is pickleball? Pickleball is a fun game that you can play for a lifetime with friends & family of all ages & skill levels. Pickleball is more than just a sport. Pickleball is a community that promotes meaningful relationships, exercise, health, wellness & most of all, FUN! Learn to play pickleball with Pickler!

layout.text: Win More Dink Battles: When to Volley & When to Bounce
